## **4.0 Tokenomics â€” The Engine of the Proof Economy**

BlockCertsAIâ€™s token architecture powers the worldâ€™s first *authenticated digital utility model*, where every transaction, AI function, and identity verification is recorded through PoA â€” not speculation, mining, or gas.

